title: NORTHEND CENTRAL PARK HOME FOR RENT
posting_body: ['9770 E. 62ND DR, Denver, CO', 'Central Park Home for Rent - $3,200/mo', 'Denver, Colorado', '9770 E 62nd Drive, Denver, CO', '$3,200 per month', 'Available Aug 5th', '3 beds, 3.5 baths', 'Approx 1,800 sq.', 'ft.', 'Owner is offering flexible term leases for those looking to buy/ build using preferred broker.', 'Stunning 3 Bed, 3.5 Bath Home with approximately 1,800 sq ft of living space located in the north end of Central Park.', 'Kitchen includes gas cook top, matching stainless appliances, breakfast bar/island and breakfast nook.', 'This home offers a concrete patio with fenced in side yard, Laundry Room with washer/dryer included, 2 car attached garage, and a beautiful xourtyard is being installed right in front of this brand new home.', 'Finished Basement has one Bedroom, full Bath, and spacious s closet.', 'Great location!', 'Walking distance to several neighborhood parks and biking/ walking paths.', 'Location convenient to Downtown, Central Park Town Center, East Bridge Town Center, Stanley Marketplace, Central Park Recreation Center, the other community pools, Dog Park, pickle ball Courts, Inspire Elementary, Primrose Daycare, Northfield Highschool, DIA & Fitzsimmons (Anschutz Medical Campus) with easy access to I-70.', 'No pets.', 'Lease Terms', 'Flexible lease terms available for those who purchase next home with my company.', '(pricing will vary, $3,200 is for 12 month+ lease)', 'Details', '3 Bed / 3.5 Baths     in the North End of Central Park', 'Rent:', '$3,200', '/month', '1,800 square feet', 'Pets Allowed: No', 'Amenities', 'Air Conditioning', 'Carpet', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Central Heat', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood Floor', 'High Ceilings', 'In Unit Laundry', 'Walk In Closet', 'Contact', 'Katie with inquiries.', 'Also check listing out on Zillow, please apply on Zillow before requesting a showing.', 'Thank you!']
